  - m_Id: 1686076216340480
    m_Localized: "Ming\r\nQu Dajun's New Accounts of Guangdong: \"Cantonese worship
      Red Emperor (Chidi) and Black Emperor (Heidi). Black Emperor governs the North
      Pole and South Sea. South Sea's waters originate from the North Pole\u2014source
      and outflow. We worship Chidi for managing the outflow and Heidi for controlling
      the source. Guangdong is a water realm; people thrive between salt tides and
      fresh tides. Unlike turtles and serpents, they transform. People credit Chidi,
      unaware of Heidi's virtue. Every household worships\u2014ritually improper,
      but this is how Cantonese honor origins.\""
