      water.\r\nBrewing: Boil water \u2192 add tea leaves to pot \u2192 pour boiling
      water over leaves.\r\nServing: Pour tea into cups to 80% capacity.\r\nEtiquette:
      Guests tap table twice with index and middle fingers when host pours tea. Other
      customs relaxed."
